@zakizhou 
 I have change the code to :
`sess.run(train_step,feed_dict={x: images, y_: labels, keep_prob: 0.5})`

But it give the same error as I pointed out before.

Also I had tried to  change the code to
 `sess.run(train_step,feed_dict={x: images.eval(), y_: labels.eval(),keep_prob:0.5})`.
But this will lead the program to execute forever. In my point the `images.eval()` step can't done forever.

Can you see my code to give me some another advice ?? Thank you so much.
